    Vector location,
    Vector velocity,
    Color color)
        Creates a new Body with the values used.
        Parameters:
        name - The Body's name (as the name of a planet...!).
        weight - The Body's weight.
        size - The Body's radius (just for circular bodies)
        location - The vector containing the position in a 2D space of the Body.
        velocity - The vector containing the velocity in a 2D space of the Body.
        color - The Body's color.
